### GET gym_space
GET {{api_url}}/gyms/1/gym_spaces/1.json
Accept: application/json

### GET all gym_spaces
GET {{api_url}}/gyms/1/gym_spaces.json
Accept: application/json

### Delete space
DELETE {{api_url}}/gyms/1/gym_spaces/{{gym_space_id}}.json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
